<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Delivered Parcel</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #FAFAFA;
            color: #222222;
        }

        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .status {
            background-color: #1E1E1E;
            color: #fff;
            width: 70px;
            padding: 10px;
            animation: blink 1s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            from{
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to{
                opacity:1;
            }
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #1E1E1E;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 14px;
            background-color: #E9EB77;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #E9EB77;
            padding: 14px;
        }

        img {
            background-color: #1E1E1E;
            padding: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="email-wrapper">

        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Delivered Parcel</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <%= sendername %>,</p>
            <p>Your parcel has been delivered:</p>
            <p>Here are the details:</p>
            <p>From: <%= from %></p>
            <p>To: <%= to %></p>
            <p>Sender: <%= sendername %></p>
            <p>Recipient: <%= recipientname %></p>
            <p>Cost: $<%= cost %></p>
            <p>Weight: <%= weight %></p>
            <p>Note: <%= note %></p>
            <p class="status">Delivered</p>
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dap91fhxh/image/upload/v1717495157/hero_r5lgvq.png" alt="" height="250px" width="500px">
            <h3>Note:</h3>
            <p>Please if you were not sending or receiving the parcel ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:alokmondala199@gmail.com">sendit@outlook.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
